                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Police Constable</hi> 100 <hi rend="italic">G</hi>). I took Howard into custody outside the Black Bull—he gave his correct address, but a wrong name.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Howard.</hi> I gave my right name, only my mother has been married twice. (<hi rend="italic">Before the Magistrate Howard said</hi>. "I had no hand in the watch. This prisoner, Hussey, gave it to Donovan, and then me and Donovan were walking away together, when Donovan dropped the watch."<hi rend="italic">Hussey said</hi>. "I had had a drop to drink, and I did not know what I was doing of.")</p>
